translations: 酪氨酸；（北欧神话）战神蒂尔

sentences.sentence: Woden, who was the father of Tyr, was the god of storms.
sentences.translation: 沃登是蒂尼的父亲，是暴风雨之神。

sentences.sentence: They built a temple at Tyr, on the last great bend in the river.
sentences.translation: 他们在河道最后一个大弯上为战神蒂尔建造了一所神庙。

sentences.sentence: In general, DCB method was the best method of esterification of Fmoc-Tyr(t-Bu)-OH and Wang resin.
sentences.translation: 总之，DCB方法是酪氨酸和王树脂成酯反应的最好方法。
